---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" language="Markdown" currentFile="personal/about.me">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-[#2b2b2b] pb-2 mb-6">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">about.me</h1>
      <span class="text-xs text-[#858585]">1.2 KB</span>
    </div>
    
    <div class="space-y-6 text-[#cccccc] leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I am a software engineer with a passion for building robust, scalable systems and intuitive user interfaces.
        My journey in tech started with tinkering on old hardware and has evolved into a career focused on modern web technologies and cloud infrastructure.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">## Philosophy</h3>
      <p>
        I believe in writing code that is not just functional, but maintainable and easy to understand. 
        "Code is read much more often than it is written."
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">## Interests (Off-Keyboard)</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li>Bouldering and indoor climbing</li>
        <li>Specialty coffee brewing (V60 enthusiast)</li>
        <li>Mechanical keyboards</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>